        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A short energy statement for the morning when the inherited belief is running loud. Say it standing, if you can: standing is the physical gesture that goes with this particular statement.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
